OL,3,CMan jailed for multiple sexual
OL,4,Coffences against children as manhunt
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FA man has been jailed for 32 years
OL,8,Fafter a two-year investigation into a
OL,9,Fstring of child sexual exploitation
OL,10,Foffences including the rape of teenage
OL,11,Fgirls.
OL,13,FTwenty-eight-year-old Bawan Hawre from
OL,14,FDoncaster was sentenced for multiple
OL,15,Fcounts of rape against teenage
OL,16,Fchildren alongside false imprisonment
OL,17,Fand possession of indecent images.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
