CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781470069
OL,3,CMan jailed for multiple sexual
OL,4,Coffences against children as manhunt
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FTwenty-one-year-old Sharam Muhamadi
OL,8,Ffrom Doncaster is currently the
OL,9,Fsubject of a manhunt by police and was
OL,10,Fconvicted in his absence of two counts
OL,11,Fof trafficking girls for exploitation.
OL,12,FHe was found guilty of multiple modern
OL,13,Fslavery offences.
OL,15,FAn investigation began in August 2024
OL,16,Fafter one victim disclosed the abuse
OL,17,Fshe has endured. Six more girls were
OL,18,Fthen identified and testified.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781470069
OL,3,CMan jailed for multiple sexual
OL,4,Coffences against children as manhunt
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FUnder the guise of fake names, Hawre,
OL,8,Fknown as 'Karo' and Muhamadi using the
OL,9,Fpseudonym 'Jack', communicated with
OL,10,Fgirls across South Yorkshire through
OL,11,Fsocial media, offering them e-
OL,12,Fcigarettes and vapes.
OL,14,FThe two men then arranged to meet the
OL,15,Fgirls in person, where they were
OL,16,Ftransported from Barnsley to Doncaster.
OL,18,FThe jury heard how the girls were
OL,19,Fgiven alcohol and drugs, after which
OL,20,Fsix of the girls were raped by Hawre.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
