OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781470069
OL,3,CMan jailed for multiple sexual
OL,4,Coffences against children as manhunt
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FDuring sentencing, some of the
OL,8,Fvictim's personal statements were read
OL,9,Fout. Her Honour Judge Sarah Wright
OL,10,Fsaid: "Their bravery in speaking up
OL,11,Fknowing that they will be asked about
OL,12,Fintimate details is considerable and
OL,13,Fcannot be underestimated."
OL,15,FDetective Sergeant Jude Proffitt from
OL,16,Fthe BSAFE investigation team, said:
OL,17,F"Not only did they have to suffer this
OL,18,Fhorrific abuse, but also relay this to
OL,19,Four detectives during the
OL,20,Finvestigation, and again to the courts.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
