FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1781470069
OL,3,CMan jailed for multiple sexual
OL,4,Coffences against children as manhunt
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,F"The courage and resilience they have
OL,8,Fshown is admirable, and is ultimately
OL,9,Fwhat secured these convictions."
OL,11,FBawan Hawre was sentenced to for:
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire police say they "will
OL,14,Fnot stop" until they find fellow
OL,15,Fpredator Sharam Muhamadi. He is due to
OL,16,Fbe sentenced at a later date.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/5
